      "value": "<p><strong>Element&nbsp;</strong>water;&nbsp;<strong>Type&nbsp;</strong>substance infusion;&nbsp;<strong>Level&nbsp;</strong>2;&nbsp;<strong>Burn&nbsp;</strong>2<br><strong>Prerequisite&nbsp;</strong>slick<br><strong>Associated Blasts&nbsp;</strong>blizzard, charged water, cold, ice, water<br><strong>Saving Throw&nbsp;</strong>Reflex negates</p>\n<p>Your blast leaves behind slippery water or ice in its area for as long as the blast is in that area and for 1 round thereafter, making the area difficult terrain and increasing the DC of Acrobatics checks attempted in the area by 5. You can use this infusion only if you also use a form infusion that has an area of effect.</p>",
